HEADWORD: Amphicome
<hw>Am"phi*come</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ with
hair all round; <grk>'amfi`</grk> + <?/ hair.]</ety> <def>A kind of
